---
title: Beef and Pesto Flatbreads with Balsamic-Dressed Garden Salad
description: Beef sautéed with onions is the perfect topper for pesto flatbreads! Finish with a sprinkling of mozzarella and Parmesan before transferring it to the oven for some melting action. A refreshing salad drizzled with balsamic glaze rounds out this delicious dinner.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/beef-and-pesto-flatbreads-58997ba5.jpg
